Class DSMConfig

      • getConfiguredApplicationRegistry

        public static IDistributedApplicationRegistry getConfiguredApplicationRegistry()
                                                                        throws DSMException
        Deprecated. in favor of newConfiguredPhysicalTopologyMonitor()
        Get the global application registry as configured in DSMProperties (dsm.properties and/or system properties) with the property named . Values of the property are as follows:
        • jcs - create a JCSTupleAppRegistry()
        • wpml - create a WPMLTupleAppRegistry()
        Upon return the registry has been started.
        Returns:
        never null;
        Throws:
        DSMException - if registry could not be created or an unrecognized configuration value.

      • newConfiguredTupleStorage

        public static ITupleStorage newConfiguredTupleStorage(java.lang.String propertyPrefix)
                                               throws DSMException
        Create a new instance of tuple storage. The TUPLE_STORAGE_PROPERTY property, with the optionally provided prefix, is consulted to select the implementation. Currently, all that is supported is the value 'jdbc'.
        Parameters:
        propertyPrefix -
        Returns:
        Throws:
        DSMException
